{"lemma":"خَطَّيْ","slug":"خَطَّيْ","root":"خ.ط.ط","root_slug":"خ-ط-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ط-ط","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":13},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11056"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to draw a line"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to draw"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to write"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to carve, inscribe"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to outline, mark"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of خَطَّ (ḵaṭṭa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"line","examples":[{"text":"وبالانتقال والفحص تبين تسرب غاز من المواسير الأرضية بخط الغاز الرئيسى المغذى للقرية.","english":"And through the passthrough and the inspection it came to light the leakage of gas from the earth pipes through the main gas supply line of the village."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stroke"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stripe"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ridge"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"handwriting"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"calligraphy"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"script"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Cognate to Nabataean Aramaic 𐢊𐢋𐢋 (“to pull out; to engrave”), Jewish Babylonian Aramaic חֲטַט (ḥăṭaṭ, “to dig out, to hollow out, to excavate”), Classical Syriac ܚܰܛ (ḥaṭṭ, “to dig out; to excavate; to carve”), Akkadian 𒄩𒁕𒂅 (ḫa-ṭa-ṭu /⁠ḫaṭāṭu⁠/, “to dig out; to dredge; to make an incision”)."},"ipa":["/xatˤ.tˤa/","/xatˤtˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11056","headword_ar":"خطّى","root":"xTw","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made to pass over:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaT~aY A@ll~`hu nawo'ahaA","text_ar":"خَطَّى ا@للّٰهُ نَوْءَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may God make, its"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a land's) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rain-giving"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"star"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asterism to pass it over, and not send rain upon it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTA^","text_ar":"خطا"},{"kind":"text","text":":) but in this case the verb is, (Mgh in that art.,) or may be, (TA ibid.,) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaT~aTa","text_ar":"خَطَّطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the final"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"T","text_ar":"ط"},{"kind":"text","text":"being changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh and TA ibid. [See 2 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTA^","text_ar":"خطا"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) Accord. to Fr,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaT~aY Als~ahoma","text_ar":"خَطَّى السَّهْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTA^","text_ar":"خطا"},{"kind":"text","text":"are syn. [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the arrow to pass over,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to miss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the mark]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTA^","text_ar":"خطا"},{"kind":"text","text":".) One says also, in praying for a man,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~iYa Eanohu Als~uwo'u","text_ar":"خُطِّىَ عَنْهُ السُّوْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May evil be made to pass him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may evil be repelled from him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and one says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~iYa Eanoka","text_ar":"خُطِّىَ عَنْكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May it be removed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put away, from thee:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~iy^a Eanoka Als~uwo'u","text_ar":"خُطِّيَ عَنْكَ السُّوْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (ISk, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTA^","text_ar":"خطا"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-  The vulgar say [to a she-ass and to a she-camel or other beast in a slippery or difficult place]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaT~iY","text_ar":"خَطِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aimo$iY","text_ar":"اِمْشِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aimo$iY ruwayadFA","text_ar":"اِمْشِى رُوَيَدًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Step thou leisurely"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: but the correct word is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AuxoTuiY","text_ar":"اُخْطُِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[imperative fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaTaA","text_ar":"خَطَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA"]}]}}